<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Credit Pog - Home</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E7D32 0%, #1B5E20 50%, #0D3D10 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #1B5E20;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .nav-link {
            color: #2E7D32;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            background: #E8F5E9;
            color: #1B5E20;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .hero {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: #2E7D32;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.4);
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #1B5E20;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(27, 94, 32, 0.5);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .info-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .info-section h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #2E7D32;
        }
        .info-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .info-section li {
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: #666;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .info-section li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-section li:before {
            content: "‚úì";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üè¶ Credit Pog</h1>
            <p>Welcome back, <strong><%= user %></strong></p>
            <div class="nav">
                <a href="/credit" class="nav-link">Credit System ‚Üí</a>
                <a href="/checks" class="nav-link">Checks ‚Üí</a>
                <a href="/logout" class="nav-link">Logout</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero">
            <h2>Borrow Digipogs with Ease</h2>
            <p>
                Credit Pog is your gateway to flexible digipog loans. Need extra digipogs? 
                Get a loan with simple 20% interest. Pay it back on your own terms, and watch 
                your credit limit grow with each successful repayment.
            </p>
            <a href="/credit" class="cta-button">Go to Credit System</a>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üí∞</div>
                <h3>Simple Loans</h3>
                <p>
                    Borrow digipogs with a fixed 20% interest rate. Start with a 250 digipog limit 
                    and watch it grow as you build your credit history.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üìà</div>
                <h3>Growing Limits</h3>
                <p>
                    Each time you successfully pay off a loan, your credit limit increases by 250 digipogs. 
                    Build your credit and unlock higher borrowing power.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üí≥</div>
                <h3>Credit Balance</h3>
                <p>
                    Overpayments are automatically credited to your account for future loan repayments. 
                    Never lose a digipog - every payment counts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Borrow:</strong> Request a loan up to your current credit limit (starts at 250 digipogs)</li>
                <li><strong>Receive:</strong> Get your digipogs instantly (after Formbar's 10% transfer tax)</li>
                <li><strong>Repay:</strong> Pay back your loan in full or partial payments at any time</li>
                <li><strong>Grow:</strong> Each paid-off loan increases your limit by +250 digipogs</li>
                <li><strong>Track:</strong> View your loan history and credit status anytime</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>Important Notes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Only one active loan allowed at a time</li>
                <li>20% interest is calculated on the principal amount</li>
                <li>Formbar applies a 10% tax on all transfers (this is automatic)</li>
                <li>You receive 90% of the loan amount, but owe the full principal + 20% interest</li>
                <li>Overpayments are credited to your account for future use</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Credit Pog System - Built for Formbar</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
